{"tid":735614,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Dse 出路簡介（100）","createTime":"2018-07-09T15:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T04:14:12.000Z","uid":193011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2506a74d7267ac7e123dcce6998a69825f7123a0","tid":735614,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:25:13.000Z","msg":"Case 1 :夠分入想讀個科 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCase 2:入左水泡想tran 科<br />\n每一間u的情況都唔同，真係要問番tran 個u 既人先知，又或者上佢個網頁睇 <a href=\"http://www6.cityu.edu.hk/arro/content.asp?cid=328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww6.cityu.edu.hk%2Farro%2Fcontent.asp%3Fcid%3D328&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=b018531a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www6.cityu.edu.hk/arro/content.asp?cid=328</a><br />\n<br />\nCase 2: 唔夠分要讀self finance (ou ,syu.....)<br />\nSf 係有機會轉ugh degrees, gpa requirement 可以係<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/732421/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/732421/page/1</a> 的non jupas 資料庫找到<br />\n<br />\nCase 3 唔夠分要retake <br />\nCase 3.1 自修<br />\n可以自己上hkeaa 自己報名，注意 報名日期十月頭就deadline <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/faq/q5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2Ftc%2FHKDSE%2Ffaq%2Fq5%2F&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=8b99df30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/faq/q5/</a><br />\nCase 3.2 日校retake<br />\n官津比較少位，多數要去直資（現代，遵理，學友社本書仔有張接受retake既直資學校list）<br />\n<br />\nCase 4 沒3322,又唔夠分，又想讀degree,hea 個大學生名就就算<br />\n有好多人都唔知可以直接用dse 報top up degree e.g cityu scope 最低入學要求5條2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 讀三年就係大學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCase 5 asso <br />\nCase 5.1 八大旗下cc開既asso(hkcc,cccu,Hku space.....)<br />\n普遍入u率係2-3成（點解某cc話自己有五成入ugc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為好多人讀唔掂，year 1就已經走左+唔係全部人都有參加個調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\nAsso上ugc 既gpa 要求：過3有機會8大<strong>（有機會）</strong>2.8 2.9有個別ugc (超級水泡科）or edu (因為要讀好多年）（2+5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&lt;2.8 ou Syu hsmc <br />\n再低少少都有top up degree 頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCase 5.2 Jupas asso /hd <br />\nPoly hd :好伏，根本個定位唔係比你上ugc <br />\nCity asso: 少少伏，有d科要同degree 仔一齊上，grade 會沒禁令<br />\n<br />\nCase 6 沒5條2<br />\n<br />\n毅進/fd &gt;asso or 黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （成績唔好太差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   ）<br />\n<br />\nCase 7 外地升學<br />\n夠分，唔夠分，有錢，沒錢都有得玩<br />\n<br />\n總結：唔好上太多x登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一試係唔會定生死<br />\n衰左dse 都仲可以入u,但係入u又唔等於賺到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論成績係點，都總會有出路，ifc 並唔係你唯一的選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0360edd73bcca058fa628866fc1f3b0bd7c673d5","tid":735614,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"讀書唔成咪走後門囉"},{"pid":"5cb10581a4670371b7da83b20f0033371b84a65a","tid":735614,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:41:27.000Z","msg":"冇做雞同做ptgf?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1df072142a3a201284728ad48800fa127372eb0","tid":735614,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0360edd73bcca058fa628866fc1f3b0bd7c673d5","tid":735614,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"讀書唔成咪走後門囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:44:33.000Z","msg":"講到asso 禁易讀,點解要去考dse入u?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通考Dse =傻人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每個人都有失敗既時刻，中學唔讀書而令到dse 衰左，係好難再再靠dse 升大學，唔通衰過一次就就永不超生，要比d老 seafood 標籤？"},{"pid":"31fd5a27ec0b2371fa9c29c2301d83d0a8773387","tid":735614,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d1df072142a3a201284728ad48800fa127372eb0","tid":735614,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0360edd73bcca058fa628866fc1f3b0bd7c673d5","tid":735614,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"讀書唔成咪走後門囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:44:33.000Z","msg":"講到asso 禁易讀,點解要去考dse入u?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通考Dse =傻人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每個人都有失敗既時刻，中學唔讀書而令到dse 衰左，係好難再再靠dse 升大學，唔通衰過一次就就永不超生，要比d老 seafood 標籤？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"主要係個人品格問題<br />\n唔少人都想堂堂正正咁考入大學<br />\n但亦有唔少人想走後門入大學<br />\n衰過無問題<br />\n只要敢再次面對(retake)就ok"},{"pid":"c9657dddaa18ad2475a5632ae613c9b641f4c413","tid":735614,"uid":18411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T16:15:08.000Z","msg":"班死毒撚真係煩撚到<br />\n平時講吓後門狗抽水咪算囉<br />\n人地認真post去分析教班中學雞<br />\n都要入黎鳩up<br />\n痴鳩線"},{"pid":"59f6d6096a6426ecda6d74343d193bc15b99bbb0","tid":735614,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31fd5a27ec0b2371fa9c29c2301d83d0a8773387","tid":735614,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d1df072142a3a201284728ad48800fa127372eb0","tid":735614,"uid":193011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0360edd73bcca058fa628866fc1f3b0bd7c673d5","tid":735614,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:25:48.000Z","msg":"讀書唔成咪走後門囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:44:33.000Z","msg":"講到asso 禁易讀,點解要去考dse入u?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通考Dse =傻人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br /